ld%20impact%20user-generated%20content%20in%20the%20near%20term.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20AI%20can't%20replace%20creativity%2C%20the%20co-CEO%20said%20during%20Tuesday's%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Swifties%2C%20Netflix%20trusts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-co-ceo-ted-sarandos-career-advice-for-young-professionals-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENetflix%20co-CEO%20Ted%20Sarandos%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20during%20Tuesday's%20earnings%20call%20that%20the%20company%20isn't%20worried%20about%20vying%20for%20more%20eyeballs%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI-generated%20content%2C%20drawing%20an%20analogy%20to%20music%20and%20Taylor%20Swift's%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20music%20is%20a%20leading%20indicator%20of%20all%20this%20%E2%80%94%20AI-generated%20music%20has%20been%20around%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20it%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20pretty%20small%20part%20of%20total%20listening%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarandos%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20established%20artists%20like%20Taylor%20Swift%20continue%20to%20be%20more%20popular%20than%20ever.%20So%20even%20in%20a%20world%20filled%20with%20AI%20music%2C%20AI%20seems%20to%20be%20mostly%20a%20tool%20for%20musicians%20to%20take%20their%20sound%20in%20new%20directions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20co-CEOs%20Sarandos%20and%20Greg%20Peters%20were%20asked%20how%20the%20streaming%20platform%20plans%20to%20leverage%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20whether%20they%20were%20concerned%20with%20increased%20competition%20for%20engagement%20with%20the%20arrival%20of%20AI%20video-producing%20tools%20such%20as%20OpenAI's%20Sora%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20apps%20like%20Sora%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-vibes-tech-founders-executives-reactions-ai-generated-content-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20AI's%20Vibes%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20made%20AI-generated%20content%20easy%20