ith%20360%C2%B0%20vertical%20coverage.%20I%20solved%20this%20problem%20by%20moving%20the%20camera%20a%20little%20farther%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%204K%20resolution%20is%20about%20twice%20as%20sharp%20as%20many%20standard%20pet%20cameras%2C%20and%20my%20cat%20remained%20crisp%20on%20screen%2C%20even%20from%20a%20distance.%20While%204K%20video%20can%20lag%20when%20streaming%20over%20weak%20WiFi%20or%20cellular%20data%2C%20you%20can%20switch%20to%20720p%20resolution%20or%20set%20it%20to%20%26quot%3BAuto%26quot%3B%20for%20smoother%20streaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20camera%20has%20the%20most%20powerful%20zoom%20I%20have%20tested.%20Even%20when%20fully%20zoomed%20in%2C%20the%20video%20was%20clear%20enough%20that%20I%20could%20spot%20small%20details%2C%20like%20leftover%20kibble%20in%20my%20cat's%20bowl%20from%2015%20feet%20away%2C%20day%20or%20night.%20Thanks%20to%20Tapo's%20smart%20pet%20tracking%2C%20I%20never%20had%20to%20pan%20or%20zoom%20manually%20to%20search%20for%20my%20cat.%20When%20the%20camera%20detects%20a%20pet%2C%20a%20magnified%20window%20pops%20up%20in%20live%20view%2C%20and%20the%20camera%20follows%20their%20movements%2C%20keeping%20them%20in%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20screen%20capture%20from%20the%20Tapo%20C260%20%20camera%20feed%20shows%20a%20pet%20food%20fountain%20with%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20kibble%20inside%2C%20placed%20on%20an%20orange%20mat%20next%20to%20a%20blue%20feeding%20tray.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f7c326cc993f9955d09794%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKibble%20in%20a%20food%20bowl%20is%20easily%20visible%20from%2015%20feet%20away%20with%20the%20zoom.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20live%20feed%20is%20always%20accessible%2C%20and%20you%20can%20connect%20multiple%20cameras%20through%20the%20app.%20I%20liked%20that%20I%20could%20swipe%20between%20feeds%20without%20returning%20to%20the%20main%20screen%2C%20which%20made%20it%20easy%20to%20check%20on%20one%20cat%20downstairs%20while%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20another%20upstairs%20with%20a%20second%20camera.%20To%20view%20recorded%20clips%2C%20you'll%20need%20a%20microSD%20card%20or%20a%20%2435%20a%20year%20subscription.%20You%20can%20also%20connect%20Tapo%20cameras%20to%20Google%20or%20Alexa%20for%20streaming%20on%20Chromecast%20or%20Echo%20Show.%20However%2C%20you%20can't%20view%20the%20live%20feed%20directly%20through%20the%20Google%20Home%20or%20Alexa%20apps.%20For%20live%20viewing%20on%20your%20phone%2C%20you'll%20need%20the%20Tapo%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20tested%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fring.com%2Fproducts%2Fpan-tilt-indoor-cam%2Fcolor%2Fwhite%2Fpower%2Fplug-in%2Fmultipack%2F1-pack%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERing%20Pan-Tilt%20Indoor%20Cam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20while%20it%20provides%20crisp%20day-and-night%20video%2C%20its%20functions%20are%20limited%20to%20home%20security.%20Since%20the%20Ring%20and%20Tapo%20C260%20cameras%20are%20similarly%20priced%2C%20Tapo's%20additional%20pet-specific%20features%20make%20it%20a%20better%20buy%20for%20pet%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b29be1e9-261b-4d90-b081-ab0a83095c60%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20with%20AI%5C%22%3EBest%20with%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-feeder%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epet%20camera%20feeders%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%E2%80%99ve%20tested%2C%20Petlibro%E2%80%99s%20video%20quality%20stands%20out.%20So%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20surprised%20when%20its%20standalone%20camera%2C%20Scout%2C%20delivered%20crisp%20footage%20day%20and%20night%2C%20with%20up%20to%205x%20zoom.%20What%20really%20sets%20Scout%20apart%20from%20other%20cameras%20is%20its%20AI%20features.%20It%20can%20recognize%20and%20track%20up%20to%20five%20pets%2C