0the%20only%20way%20to%20access%20videos%20and%20watch%20playbacks%2C%20and%20the%20plans%20are%20pricey.%20A%20standard%20AI%20plan%20gets%20you%20access%20to%20the%20last%207%20days%20of%20video%20history%2C%20and%20the%20premium%20AI%20plan%20offers%2030%20days.%20You%20can%20also%20subscribe%20to%20less%20pricey%20cloud%20storage%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20Petlibro%20app%20screenshots%20show%20a%20cat%20named%20Atlas%20drinking%20from%20a%20water%20fountain%3B%20the%20left%20screen%20logs%20the%20behavior%20under%20%26quot%3BDrinking%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20the%20right%20screen%20shows%20video%20playback%20with%20a%20timeline%20of%20recorded%20activity.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f7d2ed1c1f80efbec5fd37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWith%20a%20Petlibro%20AI%20subscription%2C%20you%20can%20access%20videos%20of%20events%20that%20have%20been%20logged%20in%20the%20app.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20a%20subscription%2C%20Scout%20offers%20access%20to%20live%20viewing%2C%20photos%20(but%20not%20videos)%20sorted%20by%20individual%20pets%2C%20and%20access%20to%20its%20AI%20assistant%2C%20Tobi.%20Tobi%20is%20helpful%20for%20simple%2C%20straightforward%20questions.%20For%20example%2C%20when%20I%20asked%20when%20a%20cat%20last%20ate%2C%20Tobi%20not%20only%20gave%20me%20the%20date%20but%20also%20offered%20recent%20photos%20(a%20feature%20available%20without%20a%20subscription)%20and%20videos%20of%20her%20eating%20(available%20only%20with%20a%20subscription).%20It%20can%20also%20tell%20you%20when%20your%20pets%20last%20played%20or%20went%20to%20the%20litter%20box%2C%20as%20long%20as%20the%20camera%20has%20a%20clear%20view%20of%20those%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20Tobi%20struggled%20with%20more%20nuanced%20questions.%20When%20I%20asked%20if%20my%20cats%20had%20scratched%20near%20the%20couch%2C%20it%20said%20no%2C%20even%20though%20they%20had%20used%20the%20scratcher%20right%20beside%20it.%20Tobi%20also%20provides%20general%20health%20information%2C%20such%20as%20whether%20your%20pet%20may%20be%20overweight%20or%20if%20their%20eating%20habits%20seem%20healthy.%20However%2C%20pet%20parents%20should%20consult%20their%20veterinarian%20rather%20than%20relying%20on%20AI%20for%20health%20evaluations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Scout%20camera%20includes%20two-way%20audio%2C%20but%20I%20prefer%20using%20the%20bird%20chirp%20sound%20to%20draw%20my%20cat%20from%20her%20hiding%20spot.%20The%20camera%20doesn't%20offer%20bark%20or%20meow%20detection%2C%20which%20could%20be%20a%20drawback%20for%20some%20pet%20parents.%20It%20also%20lacks%20treat-dispensing%2C%20but%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20recommend%20those%20extras%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20wide-angle%20home%20camera%20view%20shows%20a%20dining%20area%20with%20a%20wooden%20table%2C%20several%20chairs%2C%20and%20a%20cat%20curled%20up%20asleep%20on%20one%20chair%2C%20with%20pet%20items%20like%20a%20water%20fountain%2C%20feeding%20mat%2C%20and%20toys%20visible%20on%20the%20floor%20nearby.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f7d4aecc993f9955d099bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Scout%20camera%20was%20easy%20to%20set%20up%20and%20offered%20an%20expansive%20view%20of%20my%20dining%20area.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20long%20to%20get%20everything%20up%20and%20running.%20When%20I%20played%20the%20bird%20chirp%20call%2C%20my%20cats%20came%20right%20to%20the%20camera%20so%20I%20could%20snap%20photos%20to%20build%20their%20profiles%20and%20train%20the%20AI.%20No%20pet%20camera%E2%80%99s%20AI%20has%20been%20perfect%20in%20my%20testing%2C%20and%20Scout%20was%20no%20exception.%20Lyra%2C%20my%20short-haired%20gray-and-white%20cat%2C%20was%20sometimes%20mistaken%20for%20Atlas%2C%20my%20long-haired%20black-and-white%20cat.%20However%2C%20Scout%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20give%20feedback%2C%20and%20the%20AI%20actually%20learns%20from%20it.%20The%20more%20I%20corrected%20its%20mistakes%2C%20the%20better%20it%20became%20at%20recognizing%20my%20cats%20and%20their%20behaviors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2229de086c-bff5-4834-830d-7be091b3ebcc%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20without%20a%20subscription%5C%22%3EBest%20without%20a%20subscription%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Eufy%20E30%20is%20my%20top%20pick%20for%20a%20subscription-free%20camera%20because%20it%20offers%20customizable%20features%20I%E2%80%99d%20expect%20to%20pay%20a%20premium%20for.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20used%20Eufy%20cameras%20for%20years%20%E2%80%94%20from%20monitoring%20my%20chicken%20coop%20and%20catio%20to%20watching%20my%20cats%20indoors%20and%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20front%20door.%20I%20first%20chose%20Eufy%20for%20its%20subscription-free%20setup%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99ve%20stuck%20with%20it%20because%20it%20offers%20reliable%20connectivity%2C%20clear%20video%2C%20and%20easy%20integration%20with%20Google%20Home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20placed%20the%20E30%20camera%20in%20a%20high-traffic%20area%20to%20monitor%20my%20cats%E2%80%99%20tree%20and%20water%20fountain%2C%20and%20its%20360%C2%B0%20vertical%20and%20horizontal%20view%20let%20me%20see%20everything.%20To%20avoid%20constant%20notifications%2C%20I%20set%20motion%20alerts%20to%20pets%20only.%20It%20reliably%20alerted%20me%20as%20my%20cat%2C%20Lyra%2C%20moved%20from%20the%20cat%20tree%20to%20the%20floor%20and%20into%20her%20closet%20retreat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20notification%20from%20the%20Eufy%20app%20shows%20a%20gray%20and%20white%20cat%20perched%20on%20a%20cat%20tree%20near%20a%20window%2C%20looking%20down%2C%20with%20a%20tapestry%20and%20teal%20curtains%20v