uble%20down%26quot%3B%20until%20they%20get%20it.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20dog%20might%20bark%20louder%20or%20longer%20to%20earn%20their%20reward.%20If%20you%20give%20in%20and%20give%20them%20a%20treat%20to%20stop%20the%20barking%2C%20you've%20encouraged%20the%20escalated%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20images%20show%20a%20black%20and%20white%20cat%20near%20a%20Furbo%20pet%20camera%3A%20on%20the%20left%2C%20the%20cat%20sits%20beside%20the%20device%20on%20a%20wooden%20table%2C%20and%20on%20the%20right%2C%20a%20camera%20feed%20captures%20the%20same%20cat%20close%20to%20the%20lens%20while%20another%20cat%20watches%20from%20the%20table%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f7ca551c1f80efbec5fc3c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Furbo%20360%C2%BA%20Cat%20camera%20provides%20excellent%20video%20monitoring%2C%20but%20the%20treat-dispensing%20capability%20has%20its%20drawbacks.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20cat%20quickly%20learned%20the%20Furbo%20dispensed%20treats%20and%20became%20obsessed%20%E2%80%94%20hovering%2C%20staring%2C%20and%20eventually%20breaking%20into%20it%20with%20little%20effort.%20My%20editor%20only%20used%20the%20Furbo%20360%C2%BA%20Dog%20to%20toss%20treats%20to%20her%20pup%20a%20few%20times%2C%20knowing%20he'd%20likely%20become%20fixated%2C%20too.%20The%20toss%20itself%20can%20be%20startling%3A%20Kibble%20launched%20up%20to%208%20feet%20across%20my%20living%20room%2C%20ricocheting%20off%20walls%20and%20scattering%20under%20furniture.%20While%20some%20pets%20may%20find%20the%20foraging%20stimulating%2C%20one%20of%20my%20cats%20was%20too%20spooked%20to%20search%20for%20or%20eat%20the%20treats.%20Tossers%20aren't%20always%20consistent%20either.%20Sometimes%20they%20spit%20out%20two%20treats%2C%20other%20times%20four%2C%20so%20the%20reward%20is%20unpredictable.%20Calories%20add%20up%20quickly%20when%20too%20many%20treats%20launch%2C%20while%20too%20few%20can%20leave%20pets%20frustrated%20and%20searching%20for%20snacks%20that%20never%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Gerken%20notes%20that%20treat-tossing%20cameras%20can%20be%20useful%20for%20keeping%20pets%20occupied%20when%20they're%20left%20alone%2C%20which%20may%20help%20reduce%20problem%20behaviors%20stemming%20from%20boredom%20or%20anxiety.%20She%20says%20the%20best%20time%20to%20dispense%20a%20treat%20is%20when%20your%20pet%20is%20already%20calm%20and%20lying%20down%20or%20playing%20appropriately%2C%20as%20a%20treat%20will%20help%20encourage%20them%20to%20continue%20those%20good%20behaviors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you'd%20like%20to%20buy%20a%20treat-tossing%20camera%20for%20your%20dog%2C%20I%20recommend%20the%20Furbo%20360%C2%BA%20Dog%20Camera%20over%20the%20Petcube%20Bites%202%20Lite.%20Furbo's%20superior%20AI%20features%20(pet%20tracking%2C%20barking%20and%20chewing%20alerts%2C%20and%20an%20AI%20assistant)%20provide%20better%20insight%20for%20behavioral%20tracking%20than%20the%20PetCube.%20In%20our%20testing%2C%20the%20Petcube%20was%20unreliable%2C%20detecting%20barking%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20the%20time%20and%20failing%20to%20detect%20meows%20entirely%2C%20and%20its%20connectivity%20was%20spotty.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20Petcube's%20treat%20tosser%20was%20too%20powerful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Furbo%20360%C2%BA%20Cat%20Camera%20was%20just%20as%20reliable%20as%20the%20dog%20version%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20recommend%20it%20if%20your%20cat%20tends%20to%20break%20into%20feeders%2C%20which%2C%20in%20my%20experience%2C%20is%20the%20case%20with%20most%20cats.%20The%20Petcube%20Bites%202%20Lite%20is%20also%20not%20suitable%20for%20cats%20due%20to%20its%20powerful%2C%20startling%20treat%20launch.%20If%20you'd%20like%20to%20dispense%20small%20amounts%20of%20kibble%20as%20treats%20while%20you're%20away%20from%20home%2C%20I%20recommend%20using%20an%20automatic%20pet%20feeder.%20My%20pick%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-feeder%23best-with-camera%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20automatic%20cat%20feeder%20with%20a%20camera%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15116269706s6-20%26h%3D0f0e4aeef3b3294b424d037fb0eb8ad1bab565f3227b217b3c9190a1bf13ad3a%26postID%3D68f2b39c903e59d9ac4e6e12%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-pet-camera%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fpetlibro-granary-automatic-cat-dog%252Fdp%252F661246%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPetlibro%20Granary%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20dispense%20as%20little%20as%201%20tablespoon%20of%20kibble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22355d37f3-312c-45b7-8686-9ae19bffcb60%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20pet%20camera%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20pet%20camera%20for%20your%20home%20depends%20on%20your%20needs%20and%20preferences%2C%20but%20ultimately%2C%20it%20should%20have%20up-to-date%2C%20secure%20safety%20features.%20Based%20on%20information%20from%20my%20veterinary%20and%20tech%20sources%2C%20research%2C%20and%20testing%2C%20these%20are%20the%20key%20features%20to%20consider%20when%20choosing%20among%20the%20best%20pet%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEven%20the%20best%20pet%20cameras%20can%20be%20vulnerable%20to%20hacking%2C%20especially%20those%20that%20connect%20via%20WiFi%20rather%20than%20being%20hardwired.%20The%20good%20news%20is%20that%20purchasing%20a%20secure%20camera%20and%20keeping%20its%20software%20up%20to%20date%20can%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20risk%2C%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fashleyjallen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAshley%20Allen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20senior%20security%20engineer%20at%20Posit%20PBC%2C%20an%20open-source%20software%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20security%20features%20of%20in-home%20cameras%20you%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20overlook%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EData%20encryption%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEncryption%20scrambles%20your%20data%20so%20it%20looks%20like%20gibberish%20to%20anyone%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20key%20to%20unlock%20it.%20Even%20if%20someone%20intercepts%20your%20data%2C%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20see%20or%20use%20it%2C%20Allen%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20home%20cameras%20use%20Encryption%20Standard%20(AES)%2C%20where%20the%20service%20provider%20holds%20the%20key%20needed%20to%20unscramble%20and%20view%20your%20data.%20This%20means%20they%20can%20access%20your%20camera%20feed%20for%20troubleshooting%2C%20maintenance%2C%20or%20helping%20recover%20a%20lost%20video.%20Strict%20security%20policies%2C%20internal%20controls%2C%20and%20regulatory%20standards%20help%20prevent%20service%20providers%20from%20viewing%20your%20feed%20without%20a%20valid%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFew%20home%20security%20and%20pet%20cameras%20offer%20true%20end-to-end%20encryption%2C%20where%20you%20alone%20hold%20the%20key%20to%20access%20your%20feed%20%E2%80%94%20not%20even%20the%20service%20provider%20can%20view%20it.%20Eufy%20offers%20end-to-end%20encryption%2C%20which%20you%20must%20enable%20under%20the%20setting%20called%20%E2%80%9CAdvanced%20Encryption.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20the%20company%20warns%20that%20if%20you%20toggle%20this%20setting%20on%20and%20forget%20your%20password%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20permanently%20lose%20access%20to%20your%20data.%20Since%20Eufy%20doesn't%20have%20the%20key%20to%20unlock%20your%20encrypted%20information%2C%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20you%20recover%20your%20password%20or%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo-factor%20authentication%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Two-factor%20authentication%20(2FA)%20provides%20an%20extra%20layer%20of%20protection%20by%20requiring%20a%20second%20security%20step%20to%20unlock%20your%20account.%20Common%20methods%20include%20fingerprint%20or%20facial%20recognition%2C%20generating%20a%20one-time%20code%20from%20an%20app%20on%20your%20phone%2C%20or%20receiving%20a%20code%20via%20text%20message.%20Allen%20always%20recommends%20enabling%202FA%2C%20which%20adds%20a%20security%20step%20controlled%20solely%20by%20you%2C%20not%20the%20company.%20Even%20if%20an%20attacker%20gets%20your%20username%20and%20password%2C%20they%20still%20can%E2%80%99t%20access%20your%20account.%20For%20in-home%20cameras%2C%20Allen%20says%20that%20using%20your%20fingerprint%20or%20face%20to%20unlock%20your%20account%20is%20more%20secure%20than%20getting%20a%20code%20sent%20to%20your%20phone.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAutomatic%20firmware%20updates%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EKeeping%20your%20camera%E2%80%99s%20software%20up%20to%20date%20is%20crucial%20because%20updates%20fix%20security%20problems%20and%20ensure%20smooth%20performance.%20If%20your%20camera%20is%20running%20old%20software%20with%20known%20weaknesses%2C%20a%20hacker%20could%20take%20control%20of%20it%2C%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.securityguardsonly.com%2Fabout-us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJeff%20Ketelaars%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Security%20Guards%20Only.%20Turning%20on%20automatic%20updates%20is%20the%20easiest%20way%20to%20keep%20your%20camera%20up%20to%20date.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrivacy%20features%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EKetelaars%20says%20it%E2%80%99s%20worth%20considering%20camera%20features%20that%20help%20protect%20your%20privacy%20and%20reassure%20guests%2C%20including%20pet%20sitters.%20Options%20like%20built-in%20privacy%20screens%20or%20a%20tilt-down%20option%20physically%20block%20the%20lens%20to%20prevent%20recording.%20Bright%20spotlights%20aren%E2%80%99t%20recommended%20for%20shining%20on%20pets%2C%20but%20a%20small%20LED%20light%20that%20turns%20on%20during%20recording%20makes%20it%20clear%20when%20the%20camera%20is%20active.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVideo%20quality%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Most%20home%20cameras%20offer%20standard%201080p%20resolution%2C%20though%20a%20few%20still%20stream%20in%20720p.%20Some%20cameras%20go%20higher%2C%20but%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20better%20video%20requires%20better%20WiFi.%20Other%20useful%20features%20to%20consider%20include%20zoom%20and%20picture-in-picture%20(PIP)%20mode%2C%20which%20creates%20a%20smaller%20window%20of%20your%20camera%20feed%20on%20top%20of%20another%20screen%20or%20app.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20PIP%20mode%2C%20you%20can%20watch%20your%20pet%20in%20a%20little%20window%20while%20sending%20a%20text%20to%20your%20sitter.%20Some%20cameras%20offer%20color%20night%20vision.%20The%20Eufy%20E30%20is%20one%20such%20camera%2C%20but%20it%20relies%20on%20a%20spotlight%20that%20can%20be%20disruptive%20to%20pets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAudio%20quality%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EClear%20audio%20lets%20you%20hear%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20camera%2C%20but%20our%20experts%20recommend%20using%20two-way%20audio%20to%20speak%20to%20your%20pet%20sparingly%20%E2%80%94%20or%20not%20at%20all.%20%E2%80%9CSpeaking%20through%20the%20camera%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20usually%20have%20the%20effect%20people%20hope%20it%20will%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frescuedbytraining.com%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKate%20LaSala%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20certified%20separation%20anxiety%20trainer%20and%20founder%20of%20Rescued%20by%20Training.%20Rather%20than%20comforting%20your%20pet%2C%20Tedeschi%20says%20talking%20through%20a%20camera%20can%20confuse%20or%20frustrate%20them%20since%20they%20hear%20your%20voice%20but%20can%E2%80%99t%20find%20you.%20Some%20cameras%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20Petlibro%20Scout%20%E2%80%94%20still%20offer%20two-way%20talk%20but%20also%20feature%20pet-friendly%20sounds%20to%20get%20your%20pet%E2%80%99s%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFeatures%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIndoor%20pet%20cameras%20offer%20a%20range%20of%20features%2C%20from%20home-security-focused%20options%20such%20as%20security%20alerts%20for%20people%20at%20your%20door%20(as%20seen%20in%20Ring%20cameras)%20to%20pet-focused%20options%20with%20AI%2C%20like%20the%20Petlibro%20Scout.%20I%20named%20the%20Tapo%20C260%20the%20best%20overall%20pet%20camera%20in%20part%20because%20it%20combines%20home%20security%20and%20pet-tracking%20features%2C%20making%20it%20versatile%20for%20many%20households.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20cameras%20can%20connect%20to%20Google%20Home%20and%20Alexa%20apps%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20view%20live%20feeds%20or%20create%20routines%20through%20your%20home%20management%20system.%20But%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20always%20mean%20you%20can%20watch%20the%20feed%20on%20your%20phone%20through%20those%20apps.%20For%20example%2C%20with%20the%20Tapo%20C260%2C%20you%20can%20only%20see%20the%20live%20video%20on%20the%20Tapo%20app%20or%20if%20you%20cast%20it%20to%20a%20smart%20display%20or%20TV%20%E2%80%94%20direct%20viewing%20with%20Google%20Home%20or%20Alexa%20on%20your%20phone%20isn%E2%80%99t%20supported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20cameras%20I%20tested%2C%20the%20feature%20I%20found%20most%20useful%20was%20notification%20filtering%2C%20which%20identifies%20individual%20pets%20and%20alerts%20you%20to%20their%20movements.%20Preset%20positions%20and%20target%20zones%20were%20also%20incredibly%20useful%20for%20monitoring%20specific%20areas.%20For%20example%2C%20with%20the%20Eufy%20E30%2C%20you%20can%20save%20up%20to%20four%20positions%2C%20like%20a%20food%20or%20water%20bowl%20or%20dog%20bed%2C%20and%20quickly%20jump%20to%20those%20spots%20without%20manually%20panning%20the%20camera.%20And%20with%20custom%20target%20zones%2C%20you%20can%20tell%20the%20camera%20exactly%20where%20to%20scan%20for%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20privacy%2C%20you%20can%20physically%20close%20the%20lens%20of%20most%20cameras%20using%20the%20privacy%20shutter.%20With%20both%20the%20Eufy%20and%20Tapo%20cameras%2C%20you%20can%20digitally%20black%20out%20portions%20of%20the%20field%20of%20view%20that%20you%20don't%20want%20recorded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20cameras%20also%20claim%20to%20detect%20barks%20or%20meows%2C%20I%20found%20their%20accuracy%20to%20be%20limited%2C%20especially%20for%20cats.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20features%20that%20matter%20most%20depend%20on%20your%20needs%20and%20how%20you%20plan%20to%20use%20the%20camera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20upfront%20cost%20of%20a%20pet%20or%20home-security%20camera%20usually%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20cover%20a%20monthly%20subscription%2C%20which%20is%20often%20required%20to%20access%20recordings%2C%20enable%20specific%20motion%20or%20sound%20detection%20features%2C%20or%20unlock%20other%20advanced%20functions.%20An%20exception%20among%20the%20cameras%20I%20tested%20is%20the%20Eufy%20E30%2C%20which%20only%20requires%20a%20microSD%20card%20for%20recording%2C%20with%20no%20features%20locked%20behind%20a%20paywall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cef9bfd1-12be-40c7-b6c4-5782fa2ea5d5%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20pet%20cameras%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20my%20personal%20experience%2C%20customer%20reviews%2C%20and%20a%20close%20look%20at%20specs%2C%20I%20narrowed%20down%20an%20initial%20pool%20of%20twelve%20cameras%20to%20eight%2C%20then%20tested%20them%20for%20over%20two%20months.%20I%20developed%20a%20standardized%20testing%20process%20to%20evaluate%20the%20cameras%20and%20their%20features%2C%20drawing%20on%20insights%20from%20both%20pet%20and%20tech%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInstallation%20and%20setup%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20evaluated%20how%20easy%20each%20camera%20was%20to%20install%2C%20position%2C%20and%20connect%20it%20to%20its%20companion%20app.%20I%20timed%20the%20setup%2C%20assessed%20the%20clarity%20of%20instructions%2C%20and%20noted%20any%20issues%20I%20encountered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20explored%20the%20companion%20apps%20using%20both%20WiFi%20and%20cellular%20connections%2C%20testing%20live%20streaming%2C%20playback%2C%20settings%20navigation%2C%20and%20multi-camera%20support.%20For%20models%20compatible%20with%20Google%20Home%20and%2For%20Alexa%2C%20I%20also%20evaluated%20ease%20of%20integration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImage%20quality%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20tested%20all%20cameras%20from%20the%20same%20spot%20in%20a%20high-traffic%20corridor%20at%20the%20top%20of%20my%20stairs%2C%20where%20my%20cats%20drink%20from%20a%20floor-level%20water%20fountain%2C%20climb%20their%20cat%20tree%2C%20and%20lounge%20on%20the%20floor.%20This%20setup%20allowed%20me%20to%20directly%20compare%20video%20clarity%2C%20field%20of%20view%2C%20zoom%2C%20and%20lag%20in%20daylight%2C%20low-light%2C%20and%20nighttime%20conditions.%20For%20cameras%20with%20AI%20pet-tracking%20features%2C%20I%20also%20moved%20them%20to%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20house%20to%20capture%20a%20wider%20range%20of%20behaviors%2C%20including%20my%20cats%20eating%20at%20their%20food%20bowl%2C%20using%20their%20scratching%20post%2C%20and%20visiting%20their%20litter%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAudio%20quality%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20tested%20two-way%20talk%20and%20standard%20audio%20for%20clarity%2C%20delay%2C%20and%20background%20noise.%20My%20husband%20stood%20in%20the%20room%20with%20the%20camera%20and%20reported%20what%20he%20heard%20when%20I%20spoke%20through%20the%20camera%20from%20another%20room%20or%20outside%20the%20house.%20He%20observed%20how%20clearly%20he%20could%20hear%20me%20and%20whether%20the%20camera%20picked%20up%20background%20sounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFeatures%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Smart%20functions%20such%20as%20motion%20detection%2C%20pet%2Fperson%20recognition%2C%20barking%20or%20meowing%20alerts%2C%20and%20treat%20dispensing%20were%20tested%20for%20accuracy%2C%20usability%2C%20and%20reliability.%20For%20treat-tossing%20cameras%2C%20I%20tested%20the%20feature%2030%20times%20with%20varying%20treat%20sizes%2C%20from%20large%20dental%20kibbles%20to%20small%20kibbles%2C%20to%20check%20for%20jams%20or%20failed%20tosses.%20I%20evaluated%20barking%20and%20meowing%20detection%20by%20playing%20recordings%20of%20those%20sounds%20on%20my%20laptop%2C%20starting%20about%2030%20feet%20from%20the%20camera%20and%20gradually%20moving%20closer%20until%20the%20sound%20was%20detected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAll%20of%20the%20best%20pet%20cameras%20in%20my%20lineup%20share%20security%20protections%20like%20AES%20encryption%2C%20two-factor%20authentication%2C%20and%20automatic%20(or%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20Petlibro%20Scout%2C%20opt-in%20push)%20firmware%20updates.%20Beyond%20those%20essentials%2C%20I%20also%20dug%20into%20each%20company%E2%80%99s%20history.%20If%20I%20found%20past%20security%20issues%2C%20I%20evaluated%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20response%2C%20including%20how%20it%20strengthened%20security%20measures%20and%20reinforced%20its%20commitment%20to%20user%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22feda738c-b714-447d-a38a-baecc464165c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EPet%20camera%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20home%20pet%20monitoring%20camera%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20pet%20camera%20really%20depends%20on%20your%20individual%20needs%2C%20preferences%2C%20and%20budget.%20That%20said%2C%20my%20top%20pick%20is%20the%20Tapo%20C260%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20affordable%20and%20versatile%2C%20making%20it%20easy%20to%20adapt%20for%20your%20preferred%20use%2C%20whether%20that%E2%80%99s%20AI%20behavior%20tracking%20of%20eating%2C%20sleeping%2C%20or%20litter%20box%20use%2C%20subscription-free%20monitoring%2C%20or%20hybrid%20home%20security%20and%20pet%20monitoring%20features.%20Regardless%20of%20the%20model%2C%20the%20best%20pet%20cameras%20include%20up-to-date%20security%20features%20to%20protect%20your%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20it%20worth%20getting%20a%20pet%20camera%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EPet%20cameras%20can%20be%20fantastic%20tools%20for%20monitoring%20behaviors%20and%20capturing%20footage%20to%20share%20with%20your%20veterinarian%20or%20behaviorist.%20With%20so%20many%20models%20available%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20easy%20to%20find%20one%20that%20fits%20your%20needs%2C%20preferences%2C%20and%20budget.%20That%20said%2C%20issues%20can%20arise%20if%20owners%20become%20overly%20anxious%20about%20checking%20in%20or%20try%20to%20intervene%20with%20two-way%20talk%20or%20by%20dispensing%20treats.%20Tedeschi%20says%20giving%20a%20pet%20treats%20from%20a%20camera%20can%20be%20comforting%2C%20but%20it%20can%20also%20increase%20their%20anxiety%20if%20a%20treat%20is%20given%20when%20they're%20already%20stressed%20or%20upset.%20He%20adds%20that%20your%20pet%20can%20become%20distressed%20if%20they%20hear%20your%20voice%20through%20the%20camera%20but%20cannot%20find%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20there%20a%20camera%20to%20watch%20pets%20without%20a%20subscription%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20My%20top%20pick%20for%20a%20subscription-free%20pet%20camera%20is%20the%20Eufy%20E30%20because%20it%20includes%20pet-friendly%20features%20that%20many%20other%20models%20lock%20behind%20a%20paywall%2C%20such%20as%20pet-only%20motion%20and%20sound%20detection%2C%20motion%20tracking%2C%20and%20default%20positioning.%20You%20can%20stream%20in%20resolutions%20ranging%20from%20720p%20to%20Ultra%204K%20and%20record%20and%20review%20past%20events%20with%20a%20microSD%20card.%20Another%20option%20is%20the%20Tapo%20C260%2C%20which%20offers%20an%20optional%20subscription%20for%20cloud%20storage%20and%20playback.%20Alternatively%2C%20you%20can%20record%20and%20view%20live%20events%20by%20inserting%20a%20microSD%20card.%20All%20other%20features%20are%20available%20without%20a%20subscription%2C%20inclu