tors%20are%20eager%20to%20hear%20updates%20on%20some%20of%20the%20EV%20maker's%20big%20projects%2C%20namely%20its%20Robotaxi%20rollout%20and%20how%20it's%20incorporating%20AI%20into%20its%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20stock%20has%20had%20an%20extremely%20volatile%202025.%20It%20fell%20as%20much%20as%2047%25%20from%20January%20to%20March%20as%20investors%20worried%20about%20weak%20demand%20and%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk's%20work%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20which%20drummed%20up%20political%20protests%20and%20calls%20for%20boycotts.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20shares%20kicked%20off%20a%20100%25%20rally%20as%20investors%20bought%20the%20beaten-down%20stock%20amid%20Musk's%20renewed%20focus%20on%20the%20company%20and%20dissipating%20tariff%20headwinds.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221682%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tsla%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f7bb1ccc993f9955d0966a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221344%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWednesday's%20earnings%20update%20will%20provide%20investors%20with%20fresh%20insight%20into%20the%20company's%20direction%20and%20whether%20its%20furious%20stock%20rally%20can%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20top%20analysts%20say%20to%20look%20out%20for%20in%20the%20company's%20third-quarter%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dbfd8a26-fece-4db3-8c94-5afd6575cbca%5C%22%3EDan%20Ives%2C%20Wedbush%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIves%20says%20to%20watch%20out%20for%20what%20the%20company%20says%20about%20its%20plans%20for%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20earnings%2Fguidance%20on%20Wed%20are%20clearly%20important%20but%20take%20a%20backseat%20to%20the%20broader%20and%20important%20AI%20initiatives%20at%20Tesla%2C%26quot%3B%20Ives%20wrote%20in%20an%20October%2019%20client%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20continue%20to%20strongly%20believe%20the%20most%20important%20chapter%20in%20Tesla's%20growth%20story%20is%20now%20beginning%20with%20the%20AI%20era%20now%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BIt%20starts%20with%20autonomous%20then%20robotics%20as%20we%20believe%20the%20autonomous%20valuation%20is%20worth%20%241%20trillion%20alone%20to%20the%20Tesla%20story%20over%20the%20next%20few%20years%20that%20will%20start%20to%20get%20unlocked%20over%20the%20coming%20months.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIves%20has%20a%20price%20target%20of%20%24600%20for%20shares%20of%20Tesla%2C%20representing%20a%20gain%20of%2038%25%20from%20Tuesday's%20price.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bdc14e4e-ae9a-413b-9d33-beb69dd4bf02%5C%22%3EDave%20Sekera%2C%20Morningstar%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESekera%20advised%20investors%20to%20watch%20for%20guidance%20on%20a%20timeline%20for%20Tesla's%20Robotaxi%20rollout.%20Second%2C%20he%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20see%20an%20update%20on%20production%20of%20its%20cheapest%20vehicles%2C%20the%20Model%20Y%20and%20Model%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20moment%2C%20Sekera%20thinks%20Tesla%20stock%20is%20overpriced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20generally%20the%20market%20is%20overestimating%20the%20amount%20and%20speed%20of%20earnings%20growth%20here.%20We%20think%20that%20to%20some%20degree%2C%20the%20market%20is%20really%20pricing%20in%20Tesla%20more%20as%20an%20AI%20stock%20rather%20than%20as%20an%20operating%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20this%20week.%20%26quot%3BThe%20stock%20trades%20at%20over%20a%2070%25%20premium%20to%20our%20fair%20value.%20That%20puts%20it%20well%20into%20two-star%20territory.%20So%20yes%2C%20the%20stock%20is%20overvalued%2C%20but%20personally%2C%20I%20would%20caution%20that%20I%20don't%20think%20this%20is%20a%20stock%20to%20short.%20I%20just%20wouldn't%20bet%20against%20Elon%20Musk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2251cc2eef-83fc-4de5-83ea-0b0efb3d7de5%5C%22%3ETom%20Narayan%2C%20RBC%20Capital%20Markets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENarayan%20recently%20upped%20his%20Tesla%20price%20target%20to%20%2450