%20Altman%20announced%20ChatGPT%20Atlas%2C%20OpenAI's%20entry%20into%20the%20increasingly%20competitive%20web%20browser%20space.%20Shortly%20after%20the%20news%2C%20shares%20of%20Google%20Chrome-maker%20Alphabet%20dipped%203%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20Atlas%20combines%20multiple%20OpenAI%20products%20into%20one%2C%20bundling%20the%20chatbot%20functionality%20with%20a%20browser%20along%20with%20the%20ability%20for%20paid%20users%20to%20summon%20%26quot%3Bagent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company's%20AI%20tool%20capable%20of%20taking%20control%20of%20the%20user's%20mouse%20and%20keyboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222876%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ChatGPT%20Atlas%20web%20browser%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f7c9081c1f80efbec5fc21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221130%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20chatbot%20functionality%20of%20the%20ChatGPT%20Atlas%20web%20browser%3Cp%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20positioned%20Tuesday's%20announcement%20of%20an%20AI-infused%20web%20browser%20as%20just%20the%20beginning.%20ChatGPT%20Atlas%20went%20live%20on%20Tuesday%20afternoon%20for%20Mac%20OS%20users%20worldwide%2C%20with%20Altman%20adding%20that%20he%20hopes%20to%20expand%20to%20Windows%20and%20mobile%20devices%20%26quot%3Bas%20quickly%20as%20we%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20more%20to%20add%2C%20this%20is%20just%20early%20days%20for%20this%20project%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20said%20during%20the%20company's%20presentation.%20%26quot%3BThe%20kind%20of%20idea%20that%20we're%20excited%20about%20is%20what%20it%20means%20to%20have%20custom%20instructions%20follow%20you%20everywhere%20on%20the%20web.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20showed%20off%20functionality%20that%20showed%20how%20the%20browser%20could%20do%20a%20variety%20of%20tasks%2C%20from%20searching%20through%20browser%20history%20to%20even%20some%20agentic%20work%20like%20task%20management%2C%20which%20one%20speaker%20called%20%26quot%3Bvibe-lifeing.%26quot%3B%20Multiple%20demonstrations%20used%20Google's%20services%2C%20including%20Gmail%20and%20Google%20Docs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222722%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Agent%20mode%20of%20ChatGPT%20Atlas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f7c969cc993f9955d09864%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221120%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20agent%20mode%20of%20ChatGPT%20Atlas%20lets%20the%20AI%20take%20control%20of%20your%20mouse%20to%20complete%20online%20tasks%20on%20your%20behalf.%3Cp%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAtlas'%20agentic%20functions%20will%20be%20limited%20to%20plus%20and%20pro%20users%20%26quot%3Bfor%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20have%20this%20agent%20that%20you're%20having%20do%20things%20for%20you%2C%20getting%20to%20know%20you%20more%20and%20more%2C%20pulling%20stuff%20together%20for%20you%20proactively%2C%20finding%20things%20you%20might%20want%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20and%20bringing%20them%20together%2C%20which%20we%20showed%20a%20little%20bit%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20think%20we%20can%20push%20that%20quite%20far.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETuesday's%20announcement%20comes%20amid%20a%20flurry%20of%20deals%20and%20product%20announcements%20from%20OpenAI%2C%20ranging%20from%20an%20expanded%20partnership%20with%20Nvidia%20to%20the%20launch%20of%20Sora%202%2C%20a%20TikTok-esque%20competitor%20app%20for%20AI-generated%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeb%20browsers%20are%20increasingly%20becoming%20integrated%20with%20AI.%20Beyond%20Google's%20work%20to%20integrate%20its%20Gemini%20AI%20into%20its%20Chrome%20and%20Search%20products%2C%20Microsoft%20has%20integrated%20AI%20features%20into%20its%20Edge%20browser.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20plenty%20of%20AI%20startups%20making%20AI%20browser%20experiences%2C%20chief%20among%20them%20Perplexity%2C%20which%20recently%20launched%20its%20Comet%20Browser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20there%20was%20any%20doubt%20that%20OpenAI%20is%20hoping%20users%20will%20switch%20over%20from%20using%20Chrome%2C%20Safari%2C%20or%20Edge%2C%20a%20note%20in%20its%20Atlas%20announcement%20makes%20it%20abundantly%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSet%20ChatGPT%20as%20default%20browser%20and%20get%20boosted%20limits%20for%207%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI%20says%20on%20the%20download%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-atlas-ai-web-browser-openai-google-stock-price-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761069952000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f7c45d5dbc4fd10dab3df0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-atlas-ai-web-browser-openai-google-stock-price-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shares%20of%20Google's%20parent%20company%20took%20a%20hit%20as%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20pitched%20ChatGPT%20Atlas%20as%20the%20future%20of%20web%20browsing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-atlas-ai-web-browser-openai-google-stock-price-2025-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI%20to%20launch%20ChatGPT%20Atlas%20AI%20browser%2C%20taking%20on%20Google%20Chrome%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761069735000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2025-10%2F07%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X630%2F1759808826-8051.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fopenai-to-launch-chatgpt-atlas-ai-browser-taking-on-google-chrome-125102100965_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google's%20shares%20declined%20as%